body:
When trying to take a snapshot, starting camerad fails when trying to set the core affinity. The device is offroad, so the performance cores are not available.

@adeebshihadeh Do we want to go out of powersave mode when taking a snapshot, or gate the core affinity setting base on the `IsTakingSnapshot` param. If we choose the latter we also have to add checks around https://github.com/commaai/openpilot/pull/20996/files

Before https://github.com/commaai/openpilot/commit/84de248fa7cbee37ecb2fd6a9d4df50ba60a1e04 the result of `set_core_affinity` was never checked.
